{"abstract": "The stock of the jewelry retailer Signet rose after it agreed to buy its smaller rival Zale on Wednesday. That\u2019s what happens when the cost savings effectively cover the purchase price, writes Jeffrey Goldfarb of Reuters Breakingviews.", "web_url": "https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/02/19/signet-and-zale-deal-casts-2-other-deals-in-a-poor-light/", "snippet": "The stock of the jewelry retailer Signet rose after it agreed to buy its smaller rival Zale on Wednesday. That\u2019s what happens when the cost savings effectively cover the purchase price, writes Jeffrey Goldfarb of Reuters Breakingviews.", "lead_paragraph": "Leave it to a couple of diamond dealers to show how to make mergers and acquisitions sparkle. The stock of the jewelry retailer Signet rose after it agreed to buy its smaller rival Zale at a 41 percent premium for an enterprise value, which includes debt, of $1.4 billion. That\u2019s what happens when the cost savings effectively cover the purchase price. It makes the shareholder-unfriendly transactions involving Comcast and Jos. A. Bank all the more noticeable.", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/20/business/dbpix-kay/dbpix-kay-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 350, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/02/20/business/dbpix-kay/dbpix-kay-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 350}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/20/business/dbpix-kay/dbpix-kay-jumbo.jpg", "height": 597, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/20/business/dbpix-kay/dbpix-kay-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1195, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumb